Juveniles of 

L. punctilineatus

(12.1–15.0 mm SL; 
Fig. 1C
) were collected in July on Amami-oshima island, and fully matured females (
Fig. 3A
) collected from April to June on 
Kagoshima
mainland. The reproductive season for this species is likely to be spring to early summer.
